{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2c9f58c263","title":"毛泽东给黄炎培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d3d4934b30","index":0,"year":1952,"month":9,"day":29,"articleId":"2c9f58c263"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7030eda77e","type":"title","text":"毛泽东给黄炎培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"74a2f8934d","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"68e4f6ea1f","type":"appellation","text":"任之先生：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"ea4156cd35","type":"paragraph","text":"九月廿二日大示收到，甚谢。因与财经机关商酌，迟复为歉。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"a5cbe19c59","type":"paragraph","text":"先生所提税收，劳资两问题，确是应当注意调整的。据财委同志报告，有些已经调整，有些正在调整，有些则尚待研究调整办法。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"5ad77b2c65","type":"paragraph","text":"上次我和先生谈的关于中小工商业的几点意见，过于简单，不便发表。此类问题，宜由财经机关征询各方意见，加以处理，较为适宜。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"cfc04c977c","type":"paragraph","text":"大函及几个附件我已交付陈云薄一波诸同志负责研究去了。我处亦收到工商业者不少信件，可以看出他们对我们工作缺点的反映。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"57949ee5cb","type":"paragraph","text":"近日颇忙，稍待当约先生面叙。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"1e453fa717","type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"bccad64971","type":"appellation","text":"康吉","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"},{"id":"3796d41cab","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东九月廿九日","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263"}],"page":{"id":"4ee15dffce","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2c9f58c263","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}